      </tr>
    ))}
  </tbody>
</table>

<h2>Experiences & Facilities</h2>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Wood-Fired Sauna</strong> — Finnish-style, löyly, cold plunge, outdoor relaxation (free for guests)</li>
  <li><strong>Rescue Cats</strong> — 16 cats roaming freely, 24-hour natural interaction</li>
  <li><strong>BBQ</strong> — Local Chiba ingredients, equipment included</li>
  <li><strong>Bonfire</strong> — Free firewood, stargazing under the night sky</li>
  <li><strong>Café</strong> — Drinks with a view of the satoyama landscape</li>
</ul>

