<h2>⚠️ Good to Know Before You Visit</h2>
<ul>
  <li>Nearest convenience store is ~10 min by car (buy essentials in advance)</li>
  <li>Insects are common in summer — it's part of the nature experience</li>
  <li>Mobile reception can be weak in some areas (WiFi is available)</li>
  <li>If you have cat allergies, please contact us in advance</li>
  <li>No phone reservations — online booking only</li>
</ul>

